text: Phone Call from a Stranger is a 1952 American drama movie. It was directed by Jean Negulesco. Actors include Bette Davis, Shelley Winters, Gary Merrill, Michael Rennie, Keenan Wynn, Warren Stevens, and Beatrice Straight. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1952 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Jean Negulesco
